---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Fragment } from 'astro/jsx-runtime';

const title = "Comprehensive Guide to Gas Severance Taxes by State | Royalty Owner Insights";
const description = "Explore the complete overview of gas severance taxes across the U.S., including how they";

const content = "<div id=\"mm-0\">\n    <section id=\"tUrjlPX1ZYq4_tUrjlPX1ZYq4\"><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><h1 data-generated-css=\"brz-css-racwR\" data-uniq-id=\"vOSVI\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\">Gas Severance Tax Overview</span></h1></div></div></div><div><div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><picture><source srcset=\"/images/gas-severance.jpg, /images/gas-severance.jpg\" media=\"(min-width: 992px)\"><source srcset=\"/images/gas-severance.jpg, /images/gas-severance.jpg\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"><img srcset=\"/images/gas-severance.jpg, /images/gas-severance.jpg\" src=\"/images/gas-severance.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" title=\"gas-severance.jpg\" draggable=\"false\"></picture></div></div></div></div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-pQig2\" data-uniq-id=\"eoQNN\"><span>Most gas producing states levy a severance tax on its gas production, and those who don’t currently are thinking hard about it. Gas severance taxes are based on either the </span><em>volume</em><span> or </span><em>value</em><span> of the gas production. Royalty owners pay their pro rata share of these gas severance taxes. You’ll notice this tax burden as a deduction on your monthly royalty revenue statements.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-jBSkv\" data-uniq-id=\"cKlle\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\">No Standard Gas Severance Tax</span></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-wvOIM\" data-uniq-id=\"vnFFi\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\"> The vast majority of law affecting oil and gas production emanates from the state level. In keeping with this, gas severance taxes also are designed by individual states.There are as many rate methodologies as there are states that produce natural gas. States generally base their calculations on the value of the gas produced, the volume of gas produced, or some combination thereof.</span></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-qk90X\" data-uniq-id=\"hvAS5\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\">Various credits or lower tax rates are often allowed in situations where the tax rate might be burdensome enough such that wells might be plugged and abandoned. Examples might be: periods of low gas prices, low production rate stripper wells, or with fields deemed as tight gas.</span></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-bIuG0\" data-uniq-id=\"fG2nA\"></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-du6wj\" data-uniq-id=\"y0LHa\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\">Royalty Owners Pay Their Share of the Gas Severance Tax</span></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-cGGtr\" data-uniq-id=\"fQZaV\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\">Just as the Operator and other Working Interest parties must pay their pro rata share of gas severance taxes, so must the royalty owners. Royalty owners will notice this deduction shown on their monthly royalty revenue statement. For further reading on this, see the article </span><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"/oil-and-gas-royalty-management\" data-brz-link-type=\"page\">Oil and Gas Royalty Statement</a><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\">.</span></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-q8Fjs\" data-uniq-id=\"u52xP\"></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-xbbaw\" data-uniq-id=\"aY35A\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\">State Gas Severance Taxes</span></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-o0Fp4\" data-uniq-id=\"hiecx\"><span style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color2),1);\">Click on the links below to locate gas severance taxes by state. Iowa, New York, and Pennsylvania do not currently have a gas severance tax.</span></p></div></div></div><div><div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><ul><li data-uniq-id=\"eU5tr\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-y1gML\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.ador.state.al.us/severancetax/tableofc.html\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Alabama Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"pkXaC\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-p_mgV\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.aogc.state.ar.us/\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Arkansas Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"wotQ5\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-gMyVM\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.conservation.ca.gov/dog/pubs_stats/Pages/law_regulations.aspx\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">California Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"vitGr\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-b5IEq\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://cogcc.state.co.us/\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Colorado Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"ls1Ah\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-cS8dz\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://dor.myflorida.com/dor/tips/tip08b07-02.html\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Florida Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"i63s5\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-l1t0w\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.revenue.state.il.us/Businesses/TaxInformation/Excise/oilgas.htm\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Illinois Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"yrjVo\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-lnzmP\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.in.gov/legislative/ic/code/title6/ar8/ch1.html\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Indiana Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"vMzz3\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-feN8f\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.ksrevenue.org/taxrates.html\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kansas Gas Severance Taxes </a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"tBFBt\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-dclPp\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.lrc.ky.gov/KRS/143A00/020.PDF\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kentucky Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"sZIgl\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-apIZD\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://dnr.louisiana.gov/sec/execdiv/techasmt/facts_figures/la_severance_tax_rates.pdf\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Louisiana Gas Severance Taxes</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><ul><li data-uniq-id=\"mt4jq\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-ki5K6\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.michigan.gov/taxes/0,1607,7-238-43542_43545---,00.html\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Michigan Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"fk1Ba\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-rNGuJ\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.dor.ms.gov/taxareas/misc/oilgasgn.html\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Mississippi Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"gfu4y\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-sY0OE\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"https://kennydubose.squarespace.com/owners-guide/leased-and-producing/royalty-taxes/gas-severance-tax#%20http://revenue.mt.gov/error404.htm?aspxerrorpath=/content/processRequest.ashx\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Montana Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"sbvUQ\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-kW0O7\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.revenue.nebraska.gov/\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nebraska Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"bFYs_\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-mpald\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.nd.gov/tax/oilgas/\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">North Dakota Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"bcgyJ\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-eQi9U\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/5749\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ohio Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"etsaZ\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-y9QxC\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://www.tax.ok.gov/gp2.html\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Oklahoma Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"nVCHb\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-rTopt\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://legis.state.sd.us/statutes/DisplayStatute.aspx?Type=Statute&amp;Statute=10-39A\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">South Dakota Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"c87iG\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-gVdYz\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://tax.utah.gov/training/severance/\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Utah Gas Severance Taxes</a></li><li data-uniq-id=\"q9tdk\" data-generated-css=\"brz-css-aKAyL\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var(--brz-global-color1),1);\" href=\"http://revenue.state.wy.us/PortalVBVS/DesktopDefault.aspx?tabindex=3&amp;tabid=10#Mineral%20Tax%20Materials\" data-brz-link-type=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Wyoming Gas Severance Taxes</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-j9Mr3\" data-uniq-id=\"ttbIU\"><span>The Severance Tax Balancing Act</span></p><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-nkgvp\" data-uniq-id=\"i0V3j\"><span>Each state attempts to balance its need for revenue to run state government with the diminishing effect on the gas producing industry by placing yet another tax upon its operations within that state. This of course makes for regular political debate. Most states argue this on a regular basis, attempting to find the right balance for them.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></section>\n    <section id=\"5476867bb5c0d4e2e43a4df2533e422b_5476867bb5c0d4e2e43a4df2533e422b\"><div><div></div><div><div><div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><picture><source srcset=\"/images/Mineral